      "content": "thanks! that's super helpful. i love the part about the anglerfish. could u just wrap it up by talking a bit more about the \"vibe\" of the place? like, since it's so dark and unexplored, does it feel like there's anything else hiding in those deep, shadowy parts of the seafloor that we just haven't seen yet?",
